UniqueFlightTripCode,FlightNumber,AirportCode,StartLocation,DestinationLocation,DepartureDate,DepartureTime,ArrivalAtDestinationDate,ArrivalAtDestinationTime,numberOfTicketsAvailable
FlTrp00001,EK513,MAA,Chennai,London,10-Mar-2023,8.45AM,10-Mar-2023,4.00PM,150
