Database/csv file - CustomerDetails
CustomerID,CustomerName,AccountStatus

Database/csv file - TicketBookingHistory
TicketNumber,CustomerID,UniqueFlightTripCode,TripType,NoOfAdultPassengers,NoOfChildPassengers,NoOfInfants,MealType,MaxNoOfCheckingBags,MaxNoOfCabinBags,TicketStatus //TripType is OneWay or RoundTrip

